                     <interp inst="t17841020-28-person324" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner taken with the bundle upon him, which was given to the constable.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841020-28-person325">
                  William
