             produced the things, which were deposed to.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I went into this house, and they made me almost drunk, I was going backwards, and a man in a black coat stood on the stairs, and asked me to carry this bundle over the way, he said he lodged there; this man came and took me, I told the prosecutor where I was going.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17841020-28-verdict136" type="verdictDescription">
